Ing '''aksibal a mabie''' (''Tradescantia spathacea'' Sw.) metung yang tanaman a katutubu king Mexico a maki malaman a ''rhizome''.  Atin yang bulung a makintab a balamu espadang makapadurut king libutdad anti king rosas. Makintab la reng kayang bulung, a madalumdum anggang mala-metal a aluntyan/berdi, a aluntyan (''dark to metallic green'') king babo, at makintab a kulul ubi king lalam. Miraras lang 1 a pie (30 cm) kaba deti at 3 pulgada (7.5 cm) lapad. Mangasanting lang tanaman hardin a miraras 1 a pie (30 cm) king kátas.

